               <div class="col-md-5  col-sm-6 col-xs-12 left nopad">
                   <div class="wrap">
                        <h2 alt="Petmate's Promise" title="Petmate's Promise">Our Promise</h2>
                   <p>Petmate is a special place, where everything we make and do is about improving the quality of life for pets, and pet parents. Filled with engaging, passionate, and creative people, our promise is to design and produce products which fill a specific need. Loving pets is what we’re all about.</p>
                   <a class="shop-brands" alt="Click to Shop Petmate's brands" title="See our brands" data-bind="ccLink: {route:'/category/petmate-brands'} ">See Our Brands</a>
